snippet.title: 50 Pinch Barrage!! - for Nintendo 3DS
snippet.description:
Introducing 50 Pinch Barrage!!

50 Pinch Barrage!! is a cinematic PINCH-delivering action title that will ignite your inner adventurer.
The game calls on you to make death-defying manuevers and heroic timely decisions to overcome the seemingly endless traps and obsticles thrown at you one after the other.

You will assume the role of a treasure hunter that makes an emergency landing on a mysterious island. Do you have what it takes to get yourself out of the pinch and off the island in one piece?


Title: 50 Pinch Barrage!!
Price:
   US eShop: $2.99
   Canada eShop: $3.49
   Mexico eShop: $49.00
   Brazil eShop: R$9.00
Platform: Nintendo eShop

System: Nintendo 3DS
Release Date: Mar 12, 2015
No. of Players: 1 player
Category: Cinematic PINCH-delivering action
Publisher: MOBILE & GAME STUDIO Inc.
